metadata.name: Boring Ape Baller # 1
metadata.description:
Boring Ape Ballers is a collection of basketball themed Apes. Ballers are a derivative project based on BAYC # 3085. There are 3000 unique Ballers in this collection, each ape features numbers 00-99 from 30 different teams. Each baller is one of one rare collectible.

Minting special ballers earns rewards. See details at https://boringapeballers.com.

Minting three or more ballers whitelists your wallet for future drops!
